                &kp TILDE  &kp LT  &kp PIPE  &kp MINUS  &kp GT  &kp FSLH  &kp BSLH  &kp DOT  &kp STAR  &none  &none  &none  &kp SQT  &kp DEL  &kp LS(TAB)  &kp INS  &kp ESC  &none
