                &kp W  &_LeftPinky(C, LAYER_Enthium_Linux)  &_LeftRingy(I, LAYER_Enthium_Linux)  &_LeftMiddy(E, LAYER_Enthium_Linux)  &_LeftIndex(A, LAYER_Enthium_Linux)  &kp COMMA  &kp K  &_RightIndex(H, LAYER_Enthium_Linux)  &_RightMiddy(T, LAYER_Enthium_Linux)  &_RightRingy(N, LAYER_Enthium_Linux)  &_RightPinky(S, LAYER_Enthium_Linux)  &kp F
                &mo LAYER_Lower_Linux  &kp SQT  &kp MINUS  &kp EQUAL  &kp DOT  &kp FSLH  &thumb LAYER_Function_Linux ESC  &parang_left  &parang_right  &kp _HOME  &kp _END  &thumb LAYER_System_Linux ENTER  &kp J  &kp M  &kp G  &kp B  &kp V  &mo LAYER_Lower_Linux
